41
00:11:43,151 --> 00:11:46,380
like a big dome,

42
00:11:49,976 --> 00:11:53,028
and opened it,

43
00:11:53,658 --> 00:11:57,660
and then this torrential rain

44
00:12:00,344 --> 00:12:04,192
