344
00:58:04,605 --> 00:58:08,860
They have to change their methods

345
00:58:09,211 --> 00:58:11,719
and styles.

346
00:58:12,317 --> 00:58:16,422
They should be very mild, gentle

347
00:58:17,527 --> 00:58:20,967
and healthy people

348
00:58:23,223 --> 00:58:28,578
but at the same time they should be very
